# Regra #5 — Escopo de Responsabilidade por Modulo

> **Principio**: Cada modulo tem fronteiras bem definidas. Frontends sao camada visual pura. Toda logica de negocio pertence ao backend.

## Mapa de Responsabilidades

| Modulo | Role | Responsabilidade | NAO PODE conter |
|--------|------|-----------------|-----------------|
{{#each modules}}
{{#if (eq role "frontend")}}
| {{name}} | frontend | Layout, UX, formatacao, estados visuais, chamadas API | Calculos de dominio, validacoes de negocio, decisoes de workflow |
{{else if (eq role "backend")}}
| {{name}} | backend | Validacoes, calculos, transformacoes, regras de dominio, APIs | Logica de UI, motor/pipeline (→ agent-ai), DDL (→ database) |
{{else if (eq role "database")}}
| {{name}} | database | DDL, migrations, indices, constraints, contratos | Logica de negocio, ORM com metodos, codigo de aplicacao |
{{else if (eq role "agent-ai")}}
| {{name}} | agent-ai | Regras deterministicas, pipelines, LLM, schedulers | Logica de API/frontend, extracao de dados externos |
{{else if (eq role "mobile")}}
| {{name}} | mobile | Layout, UX nativa, GPS, fotos, push notifications | Calculos de dominio, logica de sincronizacao complexa |
{{else if (eq role "e2e")}}
| {{name}} | e2e | Features BDD, step definitions, page objects, fixtures | Codigo de aplicacao, logica de negocio |
{{else}}
| {{name}} | {{role}} | Conforme definido no CLAUDE.md | Conforme definido no CLAUDE.md |
{{/if}}
{{/each}}

## Roteamento de Escopo

```
Nova logica identificada
    ├─ Visual/UX? → Frontend
    ├─ Regra de negocio? → Backend
    ├─ Motor/pipeline/AI? → Agent-AI
    ├─ Schema/DDL? → Database
    └─ Duvida? → Backend (default seguro)
```
{{else}}
# Rule #5 — Scope of Responsibility per Module

> **Principle**: Each module has well-defined boundaries. Frontends are pure visual layer. All business logic belongs to the backend.

## Responsibility Map

| Module | Role | Responsibility | CANNOT contain |
|--------|------|---------------|----------------|
{{#each modules}}
{{#if (eq role "frontend")}}
| {{name}} | frontend | Layout, UX, formatting, visual states, API calls | Domain calculations, business validations, workflow decisions |
{{else if (eq role "backend")}}
| {{name}} | backend | Validations, calculations, transformations, domain rules, APIs | UI logic, engine/pipeline (→ agent-ai), DDL (→ database) |
{{else if (eq role "database")}}
| {{name}} | database | DDL, migrations, indexes, constraints, contracts | Business logic, ORM with methods, application code |
{{else if (eq role "agent-ai")}}
| {{name}} | agent-ai | Deterministic rules, pipelines, LLM, schedulers | API/frontend logic, external data extraction |
{{else if (eq role "mobile")}}
| {{name}} | mobile | Layout, native UX, GPS, photos, push notifications | Domain calculations, complex sync logic |
{{else if (eq role "e2e")}}
| {{name}} | e2e | BDD features, step definitions, page objects, fixtures | Application code, business logic |
{{else}}
| {{name}} | {{role}} | As defined in CLAUDE.md | As defined in CLAUDE.md |
{{/if}}
{{/each}}

## Scope Routing

```
New logic identified
    ├─ Visual/UX? → Frontend
    ├─ Business rule? → Backend
    ├─ Engine/pipeline/AI? → Agent-AI
    ├─ Schema/DDL? → Database
    └─ Uncertain? → Backend (safe default)
```
{{/if}}
